Harvard-Oxford Cortical Atlas

Source: R/data.R
hoCort.Rd

Brain atlas for the Harvard-Oxford cortical parcellation with 48 regions per hemisphere. Contains 2D polygon geometry for ggseg::geom_brain().

Usage

hoCort()

Value

A ggseg.formats::ggseg_atlas object (cortical).

References

Makris, et al. (2006) Schizophrenia research 83(2-3):155-151 (doi:10.1016/j.schres.2005.11.020 )
